        "# Initialize summarization pipeline\n",
        "summarizer = pipeline(\"summarization\", model=\"facebook/bart-large-cnn\")\n",
        "\n",
        "# Example input text (you can replace this with any article)\n",
        "input_text = \"\"\"\n",
        "Artificial intelligence (AI) is a rapidly evolving field of computer science\n",
        "concerned with building machines capable of performing tasks that typically\n",
        "require human intelligence. These tasks include problem-solving, learning,\n",
